title: How to Filter Duplicates in Excel (7 Suitable Ways)
snippet: Jun 18, 2024 · In this article, various ways to filter duplicates in excel have been described. The seven most suitable ways have been explained here.

title: Filter for or remove duplicate values - Microsoft Support
snippet: Select one or more of the check boxes, which refer to columns in the table, and then click Remove Duplicates. Tip: If the range of cells or table contains many columns and you want to only select a few columns, clear the Select All check box and select only the columns that you want.

title: Excel UNIQUE (): The Fastest Way to Filter Duplicates
snippet: Jul 25, 2025 · Discover how to use the Excel UNIQUE () function to instantly remove duplicates and extract distinct values from any list. Learn how to apply it to both rows and columns.

title: How to Filter Out Duplicates in Excel: A Step-by-Step Guide

title: How to Find Duplicates in Excel: Identify, Count & Filter
snippet: Learn how to find duplicates in Excel using simple methods. Identify, highlight, count, filter, and remove duplicate data easily for clean and accurate reports.

title: Download and install Google Chrome
snippet: If you have issues when you download Chrome on your Windows computer, use the alternative link to download Chrome on a different computer. At the bottom of the page, under 'Chrome family', select Other platforms. Select the OS of the device that you wish to install Chrome on. Move the file to the computer where you want to install Chrome.
